<div id="picture-bg"></div>

<div class="container homepage">
	<div id="home-hero">
		<h1>Create Your Own Private Label Crowdfunding Website</h1>
		<h3 style="">Free to try. Simple to setup. All on your own domain.</h3>
		<a href="#register_screen" class="btn btn-large btn-primary" id="go-button" data-toggle="modal">Get started on your campaign!</a>
	</div>


	<div class="row business-benefits">
		<div class="span5">
			<img src="/images/Coins-In-Hand.png" class="instruct-icon" alt="[__]"/>
			<h2 class="light">Competitive pricing</h2>
			<p>OpenFund <strong>takes 0.5% per transaction</strong>. If you include Stripe processing it's a <em>grand total</em> of <strong>3.4% + 30&cent; per transaction</strong>.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="span5 offset1">
			<img src="/images/Money-Dollar-2.png" class="instruct-icon" alt="[__]"/>
			<h2 class="light">Stripe integration</h2>
			<p>You to have the power <em>and security</em> - we use Stripes latest technology, <strong>Stripe Connect</strong> to process your payments through their state of the art platform.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row" style="margin-top: 10px;">
		<img src="/images/section_divider_down.png">
	</div>

	<br/>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="span12">
			<h1 class="pitch-title centered">
				Attract new customers like never before<br>
				<small>OpenFund helps you secure customers on your terms.</small>
			</h1>
			
			<br>
			<br>
			
			<div class="centered" id="screenshot-holder">
				<br/>
				<img src="/images/devices.png" id="devices"/>
				<br/>
				<br/>
				<br/>
				<a href="<%= @random_campaign.try(:full_domain) %>#" class="btn btn-info btn-large example-button">See an example campaign site</a>
			</div><!-- end of #screenshot-holder-->
		</div>
	</div><!-- end of .row-->

	<br/>
	<br/>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="centered">
			<h1 class="pitch-title">
				Your virtual store-front is ready for business.<br>
				<small>The best way to crowdfund your project is here.</small>
			</h1>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row business-benefits">
		<div class="span5">
			<img src="/images/Wand.png" class="instruct-icon" alt="[__]"/>
			<h2 class="light">Domain magic</h2>
			<p>We understand <strong>how important your brand is</strong>, so we let you host your OpenFund campaign on your domain. Just change some DNS records. <strong>No code required!</strong></p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="span5 offset1">
			<img src="/images/Places.png" class="instruct-icon" alt="[__]"/>
			<h2 class="light">Open up shop on your terms</h2>
			<p>Not everyone fits into <em>other crowdfunding sites'</em> "categories". There is no approval process for an OpenFund campaign, <strong>we only empower you</strong> to build a better world!</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row" style="margin-top: 10px;">
		<img src="/images/section_divider_down.png">
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="centered">
			<h1 class="pitch-title">What are you waiting for?</h1>
			<a href="#register_screen" class="btn btn-large btn-primary" id="go-button" data-toggle="modal">Create my OpenFund site!</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<br/>

	<div class="row" style="margin-top: 10px;">
		<img src="/images/section_divider_up.png">
	</div>

</div> <!-- end of .container-->

<div class="modal hide" id="register_screen" style="width: 254px !important; margin-left: -127px;">
	<div class="modal-header">
	  <h3 id="myModalLabel">Let's get started...</h3>
	</div>
	<div class="modal-body">
		<p style="font-size: 12px;">You're less than 5 minutes from a preview of your first campaign!</p>
	  <%= render :partial => "devise/registrations/form" %>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="modal hide" id="login_screen" style="width: 254px !important; margin-left: -127px;">
	<div class="modal-header">
	  <h3 id="myModalLabel">Log In</h3>
	</div>
	<div class="modal-body">
	  <%= render :partial => "devise/sessions/new" %>
	</div>
</div>